'''Tiṭṭ tuddist''' d yiwet n telmest n [[tiṭṭ|wallen]] ilan (yesɛan) aṭas n tniltiyin timzikin timadasin. Allen tuddisin mgaradent ɣef wallen ilan yiwet n tlintit am wallen n [[salen|yiselman]] d [[agṭiṭ|yigḍaḍ]] d wagla n [[timsuṭad|temsuḍaḍ]] s umata (gar-asent [[Afgan|amdan]]). Dɣa llant snat n tegrawin meqqren ilan allen d tuddisin: [[aburɣes|ibureɣsen]] yakk d [[tiruca]] (am [[takureẓma|tkureẓma]] d<nowiki/> [[Aẓeffun|uẓeffun]].

Amḍan n tniltiyin deg wallen tuddisin iga gar n ddaw n 100 alamma d ugar m 20,000 deg telmas yemgaraden n [[iɣersiwen]], u yal tiniltit tga d amur n ufella seg tmuski yettusemman [[taṭṭiwt]]. S deffir n tniltit, tgebber teṭṭiwt seg kra n [[takwatt|tekwatin]] tinnefrayin i tafat.

